Body: Description: After updating NEA to the current version, the sharepoint jobs are not scanning anymore. The agents were updated on the servers and the proxies also. Error message: Agent Service WSB-GROUPSHARE.RKW.INT already executing scan for host WSB-GROUPSHARE.RKW.INT PrepareTask for DC 'SHAREPOINTACCESS' for task 'SharePoint Scan' failed: Unspecified error
Steps to Reproduce Updated: Run a SPAA scan to get an error after an upgrade
What We've Learned Updated: Agents are unrepsonsive?
Next Steps Updated: Reinstallation of the agents (manual)
